item.title: Tutorials in NIPS 2016
item.description: This is a collection of all material I was able to find for various tutorials of NIPS 2016 for people who were not able to attend it and are really excited to know whats going on and can’t wait for official videos and slides. Crowdsourcing: Beyond Label Generation Link Variational Inference: Foundations and Modern Methods Slides Deep Reinforcement Learning Through Policy Optimization Slides Nuts and Bolts of Building Applications using Deep Learning - Andrew Ng Slides Video from talk by Andrew Ng on same talk but somewhere else is here
